          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The energy spectra of photons from the reaction",
                " B-11(gamma,xgamma') have been  studied  at",
                " bremsstrahlung end-point energies Eg-max = 20 and",
                " 32 MeV.",
                "The 1.5-10.0 MeV secondary photons were detected at",
                " 135.0 degree relative to the incident beam.",
                "In the spectrum a line has been observed at Eg-max =",
                " 32 MeV which corresponds to 8.47 MeV total binding",
                " energy of the H3 nucleus produced in the reaction",
                " B11(gamma,t+gamma').  The absence of the 8.47 MeV",
                " line in the spectrum of possible final nuclei states",
                " gives rise to the suggestion that this line is",
                " associated with the reaction mechanism."
              ]
            }
          ],
